oai_dc:dc.dc:title: A Case Description of Possible Vitamin-E Deficiency among Calves in a Large Danish Dairy Herd: Clinical Findings, Supplementation and Future Prevention
oai_dc:dc.dc:creator: Engelbrecht, R.
Krogh Jensen, S.
Linde, E.
Myrup Pedersen, K.
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Denmark
hypovitaminosis E
calves
pneumonia
herd health
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: The objective with the present report is to present a case of what seemed to be hypovitaminosis E among two ten-week-old dairy calves (mainly due to pneumonia) in a 900-cow Danish dairy herd.
